  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>There may be situations where you need to transfer cash from a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT), such as moving cash to a safe or making payouts to reimburse for services or supplies. Users with a Shift Lead, Manager, or higher role can perform these tasks, including transferring cash between VCTs or pulling cash from a VCT.</p><h3 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)CashTransfers-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2717089793\" rel=\"nofollow\">Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933901843/Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+Setup\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933901843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Setting up a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933639827\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assign a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT) to Accept Payments</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541484/Configuring+a+Cash+Drawer+to+Open+Automatically+When+a+Receipt+is+Printed\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541484\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Configure a Cash Drawer to Open Automatically When a Receipt is Printed</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541639/Close+Reconcile+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Closing a Virtual Cash Terminal (VCT)</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229524/Reports+Cash+Reconciliation\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Cash Reconciliation</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933803641/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)CashTransfers-PerformaCashTransfer\">Perform a Cash Transfer</h2><p>Log into a computer with <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933639827/Assign+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal+VCT+to+Accept+Payments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933639827\" data-linked-resource-version=\"22\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">an assigned VCT.</a> On the Navigation Bar, click the <strong>Location Short Name</strong> to expand a list of options. On the dropdown, click <strong>Cash Transfer</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"340\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933803641/Transfer%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>On the Cash Transfer pop-up, fill out the necessary information including whether you are adding or removing funds from the VCT, the Amount, the Destination or Source, and any notes for the transfer. Click <strong>Transfer Cash</strong> to confirm the transfer. A confirmation alert will notify you of the new cash balance of the VCT.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Add/Remove</strong> - Select whether you are adding cash to this VCT or removing cash from this VCT.</p></li><li><p><strong>Amount </strong>- Enter the amount that will be added to the VCT or subtracted from the VCT.</p></li><li><p><strong>From Source/To Destination</strong> - Select the Source when adding cash to the VCT or the Destination if removing cash from the VCT.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Open VCT</strong> - Cash can only be transferred between VCTs when multiple terminals are assigned. </p></li><li><p><strong>Not a VCT</strong> - Use when transferring to an outside source (Safe, Bank Deposit, etc.).</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Notes </strong>- Add any additional notes to help log details about the transfer.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933803641/Transfer%204.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933803641/Transfer%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"VirtualCashTerminal(VCT)CashTransfers-ReconciliationReportCashTransfers\">Reconciliation Report Cash Transfers</h3><p>When <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541639/Close+Reconcile+a+Virtual+Cash+Terminal\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541639\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">closing your VCT</a>, any transfers will be recorded in the Transfers tab of the Reconciliation Report.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933803641/Transfer%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
